erHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"a7afea6a81c1671d8f1b4144d3c5429c32b0ed66","tid":1777644,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:53:43.000Z","msg":"小妹第一次做愛🙈🙈<br />\n係男朋友屋企🙈🙈<br />\n好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce2d73ee18473ce60a154a1c09f45e218c97838","tid":1777644,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:30:37.000Z","msg":"第一次自己一個去旅行<br />\n感覺好爽 無咩束縛<br />\n安排行程唔使遷就團友<br />\n可以隨便認識陌生人 同陌生人組團玩<br />\n拍左拖之後唔使諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba79400ec3f92c2ed0b03b1457a21b970a57028","tid":1777644,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:41:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3caQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=e9421377\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"177e4531d38f46c5010bb568d24441fc71eed0a4","tid":1777644,"uid":174926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"第一次聽國歌聽到喊"},{"pid":"8e417a2d7286c8a05c1526cf7220318badeea365","tid":1777644,"uid":168730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"環保吹?"},{"pid":"45abebfc6f85bdf16753b6e0aa8cd185b03679da","tid":1777644,"uid":261505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"第一次同男朋友做愛 大家都係處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢射完之後到我射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade3faa8c19f9504e440fe7dd00c98f47db48c83","tid":1777644,"uid":204917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:16:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3da0e53a5d92071b68d6c6619f0ecb084578d7e9","tid":1777644,"uid":301064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45abebfc6f85bdf16753b6e0aa8cd185b03679da","tid":1777644,"uid":261505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"第一次同男朋友做愛 大家都係處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢射完之後到我射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}